Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HC0B5C2&}"Keep Out. -Birdman"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No response, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no pedals. It looks like a glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter. Let us make it our jurisdiction regardless of its lack of wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shadowy business role is as the Master Sergeant of the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sell off illegally parked bicycles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and am using that as the basis for forming my gorgeous rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious sake, food, women flocking to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The business may have a bit of a bad reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the way of the world is the greater villainy, the greater glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my pick of raven-haired maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the money, I can have anything I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant, a woman from Birdman is coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, some woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost to Lake Biwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the plane that we all made together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be sold for a high price to a certain important person in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make an even better plane,\N we could sell it for even more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about I become your sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is all a power game, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as pure love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is nothing but a fleeting illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realize the truth about society, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing in this world that cannot be bought with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is this pain I feel in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H6C00C6&\fad(200,0)}J{\c&H000000&}-pwq
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before me lay open innumerable doors to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had already come to my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the many fliers, only one was conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sink or swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(640,531)\3c&H1B0F3A&\c&H0B00DE&\be1\fad(0,1400)}"Secret Society\N Lucky Cat\N Chinese Restaurant"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can learn the other sides of a lot of different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a fun experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what does "Secret Society" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, we have a prospective new hire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Aijima, the manager of Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please read this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually expect an organization that wrote "Secret Society" on their flier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to actually be a secret society,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant is one, exactly as the sign said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their branches include the Library Police, the Print Shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps, and a bunch of other unofficial circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taken all together, they are the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they have a hand in all the business at the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is the organization that essentially controls the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, once you've read the menu you will not be allowed to quit our organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do quit the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a little process called "paying the bill" will be waiting to erase you from society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gather every single piece of personal information about the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which videos you rented from the video rental store,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what you bought from the supermarket or convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which books you read, which transmissions you sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even what you smelled like when you were a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no intention of turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show them all by climbing to the top of this Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good look you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now I will assign you to the Library Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to have you on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There stood an ominous man with an evil face of ill portent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that man has made a giant plaything out of my fate ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The original aim of the Library Police
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to chase down the scoundrels who had not returned materials to the library
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to recover the lent books by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the goal eventually deviated from how it had started,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most people's secret and personal information
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were accumulated by the Library Police--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people both inside and outside of Kyoto, from Oohara's Sanzen Temple in the north
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Uiji's Byoudou Temple's Houou Hall in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now even an organization that helps participate in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, those who control information, control the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will rise in rank,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get to a place where I can handle all the information I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I quickly ran into a strange individual whom I was to collect from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi Seitarou, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That copy of Jules Verne's 20,000 Leagues Under the Sea is more than a year overdue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your duty as a library patron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi-san, it's way past the due date, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is... But just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been four months since you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta hit the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, unable to collect a single book for more than a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won fame as the greatest failure in the history of the Library Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, Ozu used all kinds of techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to recover books from the evil overduers and was promoted for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, he spun an unfathomable web of human connections,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rose even in his first year to become the right hand man to Aijima-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why does a human like you end up being promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unimpeachable character, conversational skills, clear thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a cute appearance, and copious amounts of overflowing love for your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the secrets to being loved by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'll kill you, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to live some meaningless life enjoying the unhappiness of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so very awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, no matter how hard you work, I'll do my best to make sure you turn out no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are tied together by a dark thread, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\c&HA567D6&\fad(0,200)}"Philippine Trench"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't until far later that I came to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Mr. Higuchi's impromptu escapes were aided by Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in the way, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. He's my Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord0\c&HF9FBF4&\pos(762,608)}"Brand New"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please overlook it.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that'll cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,June of my second year, finally realizing I had no talent at collecting books,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "restaurant" transferred me to the Print Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Print Shop is an organization in control of many excellent students
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which mass produces fraudulent reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always at hand to save students facing a crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my job was to deliver the finished reports to the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get promoted faster,\N I took on a large number of customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,delivering reports using a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that incident, over 200 students failed credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the worst disaster in the history of the Print Shop, and it lost the customers' faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was an acquaintance of Ozu, he couldn't be so obvious about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Aijima-senpai had been putting more and more distance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then spoke to me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a side job. Help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-senpai's front
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the President of the library and supervisor of the Movie Circle Misogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the jester in Mr. Jougasaki's court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission was to collect information on a new recruit and allow him to approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you do on the weekends, Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to tell you something like that, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and go search!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-M-M-M-Mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're called Mochiguman and they come in sets of five...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? One's missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I think something flew off when you fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, it's dangerous. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but it's always come back to me, even if I didn't search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, having broken Aijima-senpai's mood, was demoted to the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps is a group that manages the illegal parking of bicycles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is a major source of funds for the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weak-kneed wimp! Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This organization does not suit my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of revealing Aijima and all the crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant has committed through the years and escaping...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.86,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous. You'll end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H020705&\bord0\pos(374,576)}"Squish"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now I'm using brilliant maneuvers to cover for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try being a little grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grateful? Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-senpai is definitely trouble, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interested in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really... Though, where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched it out using the information network of the Library Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Akashi-san said she lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed the clues, but it was quite the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like it was wandering around trying to be picked up by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very busy playing the game of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, I can't just... So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dutch wife we're targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki has named it Kaori, and we're going to take it from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to earn the respect of Akashi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-senpai decided to play a prank on Mr. Jougasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people know of the depressing things called "Dutch Wives" in this world. Even I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this elegant expression Kaori-san has?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the face that speaks out to the corrupt morals of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The carefully combed hair, the exquisitely prepared dress....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They showed the depth of Mr. Jougasaki's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I, as a human being, allow the delicate and subtle world these two created to be destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is the height of heresy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapping Kaori-san and using her to threaten Mr. Jougasaki I will not allow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let this happen! It is a very refined, pure love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand loving some doll that's not alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even put lipstick on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stepping on other people's pure love for the sake of your own desire is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting your private desires influence your public missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to lay a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did not say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I instead chose a strategic withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be a part of something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had finally gone and done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely be erased from society by Aijima's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, opportunity is always dangling in front of your eyes. Please grab onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 9,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost 5 figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran and hid in a manga café on Kitashira River, shaking like a newborn fawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one came after me, and a week afterward Aijima-senpai lost his standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF3E5EF&}"New Hero -- Bra-man!"\N "Aijima Bra-man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF3E5EF&}"Stop the Filming!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF3E5EF&}"Animal Abuse!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF3E5EF&}"Lipstick Licker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF3E5EF&}"Watch out for the ladies' locker room!"\N "Spits in your tea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF3E5EF&\fad(0,1100)}"Crazy Fetishist! Panty Sniffer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become the Manager of the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now now, don't give me a bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aijima-senpai was running the organization for his personal use,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I spoke with the executive board of the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was vaguely apprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I be but a Renaissance man of fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time you take this lucky chance to enjoy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\c&HFAFAFA&}"Ozu Establishes his Government"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I assumed the office of the Master Sergeant of the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first I was somewhat skeptical of this activity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I became more and more absorbed in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,directing it with a passion to take back the two previous years that had gone wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization acted exactly as I desired. It felt quite good, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be that rose-colored campus life I wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cornucopia of raven-haired maidens to choose from!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be my ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was no easy task getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had finally obtained it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,78)\c&H142093&\3c&HBEF7F9&\bord1\be1}"Go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(988,78)\c&H142093&\3c&HBEF7F9&\bord1\be1}"Get a move on!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all too easy to grasp once I tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had once been led astray by an adherence to pure love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally realized. Everything in this world revolved around money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sergeant, I have something excellent to tell you of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be quite profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in the Birdman Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the result, as you clearly saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have had everything I wanted. Did I make a mistake somewhere, somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! I have finished! I'm finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This. This morning I finished my journey of more than two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so moved I wanted to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was some good times, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am hungry. Would you like to go eat some ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, when I left the university a few days ago I ran into an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were not looking so comfortable at all, and hurried off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're in the same year as you, Master, they're probably a doctoral student now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder they felt awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they be embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not them who had to repeat classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is the very reason you are the Master, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about this for quite a while, but now my mind is made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soon be the day for me to go forth, out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will circle the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like something went awry with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life has not yet begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are spending overtime inside of your mother's belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I successfully obtained a life that people would be jealous of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be some more meaningful life out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More rose-colored, more sparkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might have been some
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,college life with not a single dark cloud that would have satisfied me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Are you half asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to where I am by believing in my own potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I'm saying it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why does my heart feel so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's a choice I should have made that would have led to some other possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the choices I made in my first year were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot use the word "possibility" without limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become a bunny girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become a pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become a famous singer, or a superhero who saves the world with his powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you keep focusing your gaze on that which is unrealistic, you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The root of all your evil
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in always relying on one of your other possibilities to get your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must accept that you are the person here, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you cannot become anyone else other than that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that you can lead some worthwhile college life and feel satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it, so have confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because there is nothing rose-colored in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is all a bunch of colors mixed up, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what perfect timing, meeting you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you were pretty cool until you ran away from Aijima-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fooled by Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met him, I wouldn't have completely wasted these two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's selfish and arrogant, lazy and perverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He eats people's unhappiness with three helpings of rice, and that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his feelings are pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Ozu-kun feels about his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never believe that Ozu would have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he met her as a freshman in the tennis circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went with her to see the Gozan festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were tossed around in the crowd of people and she ended up crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year he plans to see all five mountains at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any place you can see all five at once from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not unless you're in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu used the members of the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant for his own personal uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mixed up his private and public duties too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's snuck into the Honwaka Group's headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is planning on stealing the airship there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he hid his tracks, but I know he has a woman there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\c&HD1FEF9&\3c&H689DDF&\be4\fad(100,100)}"Illegal Distribution of Funds"\N "To Honwaka..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\c&HD1FEF9&\3c&H689DDF&\be4\fad(100,100)}"Steal Airship"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the daughter of the head of Honwaka Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning on using that airship for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\c&HD1FEF9&\3c&H689DDF&\be4\fad(100,100)}"Honwaka's Daughter?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\c&HD1FEF9&\3c&H689DDF&\be4\fad(100,100)}"You've got to be kidding me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was indeed a bolt out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I had misjudged Ozu all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was his rise to the top all for such a pure reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His goal wasn't simply to spend his time meaninglessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He plans to take off from here and pick up the girl in the facility on the next mountain over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, especially, I won't let you get your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite the persistent one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\c&HFAFAFA&}"Ozu had a girlfriend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crashed! Surround the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I had done had all been meaningless,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had thought that it was the same for Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ozu had enjoyed his meaningless campus life to his heart's content,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he had a girlfriend, and was even a fool in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I the only one who wasted his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately after I was born, I was the incarnation of innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loved as much as baby Hikaru Genji was by Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With not a hint of a wicked thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was said my smile would illuminate the countryside around my hometown with the light of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what of me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how you plan to settle your accounts, as you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the one responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it will always turn out like this, then I should do nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be best not to set foot outside of the 4.5 tatami room!
